Re: please help 聴解 is too hard
by Hyperworm » Tue 07.13.2010 10:17 am 1:45 素早く運べる or something else with potential tense... it's noisy at the end and I can't hear it properly1:57 これだけいろんな店あるわけでしょう2:06 やりやすそう3:04 it sounds to me like なんでピアス取ったろう？！ but I'm not sure that's grammatical 4:17 周３は来れますNot easy. I had to listen several times x.x;
